            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1475,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01Qes5JmgddwKsZSak8vxtHm\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01PoTYSBhnFkgak3BimFeSDa\",\"name\":\"extract-3\",\"input\":{\"type\":\"reply\",\"text\":\"I love the enthusiasm! But let's dig deeper—\\\"I like pasta\\\" is a personal preference, not a business idea yet. \\n\\nTo build something people will actually pay for, we need to understand: **What's the business opportunity here?** Are you thinking about selling pasta? Creating a pasta delivery service? A pasta-making course? A restaurant? Something else entirely?\\n\\nHelp me understand your core business idea—what problem are you solving, or what need are you filling?\",\"examples\":[\"A subscription box that delivers fresh, artisanal pasta from local makers to your door each month\",\"An online platform where home cooks can learn traditional Italian pasta-making techniques from master chefs\",\"A fast-casual restaurant concept that serves elevated pasta dishes at affordable prices\",\"A B2B supplier of specialty pasta to high-end restaurants looking for unique, hard-to-find varieties\"],\"conclusion\":\"Give me the real business idea—what are you actually building or selling?\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2705,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":285,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
