            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1365,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01PoEYs91CeeQqEAPVJBSPAz\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01VfKKa82rq545KvrFNwv99E\",\"name\":\"extract-7\",\"input\":{\"type\":\"reply\",\"text\":\"Great! Now let's dig into your **audience**. \\n\\nWho are we really talking to here? Are we marketing to podcast hosts, or to potential guests? And what's keeping them up at night?\\n\\nFor hosts specifically: What's their biggest frustration? Is it just the time spent searching, or is there something deeper—like finding guests who actually fit their show's vibe, or guests who flake out, or something else?\\n\\nHelp me understand the core pain point we're solving for your primary audience.\",\"examples\":[\"Podcast hosts are frustrated because they spend 5+ hours per week manually searching for guests, vetting them, and dealing with no-shows\",\"Podcast hosts struggle to find guests who are actually relevant to their niche and have an engaged audience\",\"Podcast hosts want to grow their show but don't have the network or connections to book quality guests consistently\"]}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3041,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":253,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
