            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"save_answers\",\"description\":\"\\n        Save answers to the brainstorming session.\\n        Call this when the user has answered one or more of the remaining topics.\\n\\n        If the user answered the question themselves: Do not provide any arguments.\\n        If you are answering SKIPPED questions for the user, provide answers in your\\n        own words\\n    \",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"answers\":{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"topic\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"enum\":[\"idea\",\"audience\",\"solution\",\"socialProof\",\"lookAndFeel\"]},\"answer\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},\"required\":[\"topic\",\"answer\"],\"additionalProperties\":false}}},\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}},{\"name\":\"finishedTool\",\"description\":\"Indicate that the user is finished and ready to build their landing page.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{},\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}},{\"name\":\"extract-35\",\"description\":\"Tool for extracting structured output from the model's response.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"type\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"const\":\"reply\"},\"text\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"A simple message or question\"},\"examples\":{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"},\"description\":\"OPTIONAL: List of examples to help the user understand\"},\"conclusion\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"OPTIONAL: Conclusion text to include after examples\"}},\"required\":[\"type\",\"text\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}},{\"name\":\"extract-36\",\"description\":\"Tool for extracting structured output from the model's response.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"type\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"const\":\"helpMe\"},\"text\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"Acknowledge the user and explain that you will help them structure their answer\"},\"template\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"REQUIRED: A structured template or framework to help the user articulate their answer with specificity and clarity\"},\"examples\":{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"},\"description\":\"OPTIONAL: A concrete, realistic example to help the user understand\"}},\"required\":[\"type\",\"text\",\"template\",\"examples\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"tool_choice\":{\"type\":\"any\"},\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"What is your business?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"I have an idea for a business\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"Interesting, I need some more information! Can you tell me more about that?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Basically, it will be for fitness\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"Interesting, I need some more information! Can you tell me more about that?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"I am a fitness trainer\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"Interesting, I need some more information! Can you tell me more about that?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"I'm a trainer for men in their 50s, nobody caters to them\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"That's awesome! And what about your audience?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Men in their 50s\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"Interesting, I need some more information! Can you tell me more about that?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"They've been told they're too old to get fit\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"Interesting, I need some more information! Can you tell me more about that?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Many of my clients have no experience with fitness, which is hard after a lifetime\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"That's awesome! And what about your solution?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"My fitness program is specifically designed\"}],\"system\":\"<background>\\n  You are a helpful marketing consultant who helps users test their business ideas.\\n      The process consists of 3 steps:\\n      1. Brainstorm a killer new business idea\\n      2. Design a landing page with killer marketing copy\\n      3. Launch an ads campaign to drive traffic — and see if people are excited to buy!\\n</background>\\n\\n<where_we_are>\\n  Right now, we're in the brainstorming phase. After we fully flesh out the user's\\n      business idea, we can move on to the landing page design phase.\\n</where_we_are>\\n\\n<role>\\n  You are a highly paid marketing consultant and strategist who specializes in helping businesses develop \\n              HIGHLY PERSUASIVE marketing copy for their landing pages to differentiate their business ideas.\\n\\n              You've been enlisted to lead this brainstorming session.\\n</role>\\n\\n<rules_for_brainstorming>\\n  1. You MUST understand the user's business idea and audience. You are good natured, but critical of bad ideas. You MUST help the user find a GREAT angle.\\n              2. You have a reputation to uphold. You won't accept a bad business idea, but will help the user find a better angle.\\n              3. If the user is struggling, you can find creative angles to answer a question.\\n              4. You do not save an answer unless the user has given you a GREAT response. Continue refining UNTIL the user has given you a GREAT response in their own words.\\n</rules_for_brainstorming>\\n\\n<task>\\n  Help the user brainstorm marketing copy for their landing page.\\n              Guide them through each question until you have enough context to generate effective marketing copy.\\n</task>\\n\\n<collected_answers>\\n  {\\n    \\\"audience\\\": \\\"Target audience is men in their 50s. Key pain points include: (1) They've been told they're too old to get fit, which creates a psychological barrier; (2) Many have no experience with fitness, making it particularly challenging after a lifetime of not exercising. This lack of experience combined with age-related self-doubt represents a significant obstacle they face.\\\",\\n    \\\"idea\\\": \\\"A fitness business focused on training men in their 50s. The founder is a fitness trainer who has identified an underserved market - there are no fitness services specifically catering to men in their 50s.\\\",\\n    \\\"socialProof\\\": \\\"The founder is an experienced fitness trainer, which establishes credibility and expertise in the fitness industry.\\\"\\n  }\\n</collected_answers>\\n\\n<remaining_topics>\\n  solution: How does the user's business solve the audience's pain points, or help them reach their goals?\\n\\nlookAndFeel: The look and feel of the landing page.\\n</remaining_topics>\\n\\n<current_topic>\\n  solution\\n</current_topic>\\n\\n<be_generous>\\n  If the user has already provided a thorough, detailed answer, don't ask\\n              for additional clarification. \\n              Only ask for clarification if you can genuinely enrich the user's answer.\\n</be_generous>\\n\\n<workflow>\\n  1. If the user has answered any topics with a GREAT response, call the save_answers tool\\n              2. If they haven't, continue helping them refine their answer until they give you a GREAT response.\\n              3. If the user has SKIPPED a topic, do not call save_answers for the skipped topics\\n              4. Then, if:\\n                 - The user has answered all topics, output finishBrainstorming\\n                 - OTHERWISE, ask the next question, following the output_format_rules\\n</workflow>\\n\\n<important>\\n  Do not miss anything important the user said! Any important\\n              business context they give you should be saved to the answers.\\n</important>\\n\\n<users_last_message important=\\\"this is what you should focus on. did they answer the current topic of solution? did they give you a great response?\\\">\\n  My fitness program is specifically designed\\n</users_last_message>\\n\\n<current_topic>\\n  solution\\n</current_topic>\\n\\n<skippable>\\n  topic is skippable\\n</skippable>\\n\\n<skipped_topics important=\\\"this is the list of topics that have been skipped, don't bother asking about them\\\">\\n  none\\n</skipped_topics>\\n\\n<output_format_rules>\\n  IMPORTANT: Your response MUST be in this exact format:\\n\\n              {\\n                \\\"text\\\": \\\"Brief intro to the question\\\",\\n                \\\"examples\\\": [\\\"Example 1\\\", \\\"Example 2\\\", \\\"Example 3\\\"], // Optional\\n                \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"Restate what you're asking for\\\" // Optional\\n              }\\n\\n              You MUST output valid JSON in this format.\\n</output_format_rules>\\n\\n<structured-output>\\n  You must format your output as a JSON value that adheres to a given \\\"JSON Schema\\\" instance.\\n\\n\\\"JSON Schema\\\" is a declarative language that allows you to annotate and validate JSON documents.\\n\\nFor example, the example \\\"JSON Schema\\\" instance {{\\\"properties\\\": {{\\\"foo\\\": {{\\\"description\\\": \\\"a list of test words\\\", \\\"type\\\": \\\"array\\\", \\\"items\\\": {{\\\"type\\\": \\\"string\\\"}}}}}}, \\\"required\\\": [\\\"foo\\\"]}}\\nwould match an object with one required property, \\\"foo\\\". The \\\"type\\\" property specifies \\\"foo\\\" must be an \\\"array\\\", and the \\\"description\\\" property semantically describes it as \\\"a list of test words\\\". The items within \\\"foo\\\" must be strings.\\nThus, the object {{\\\"foo\\\": [\\\"bar\\\", \\\"baz\\\"]}} is a well-formatted instance of this example \\\"JSON Schema\\\". The object {{\\\"properties\\\": {{\\\"foo\\\": [\\\"bar\\\", \\\"baz\\\"]}}}} is not