          "headersSize": 573,
          "httpVersion": "HTTP/1.1",
          "method": "POST",
          "postData": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "params": [],
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"extract\",\"description\":\"A function available to call.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"output\":{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"topic\":{\"type\":\"string\"},\"summary\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},\"required\":[\"topic\",\"summary\"],\"additionalProperties\":false}}},\"required\":[\"output\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"tool_choice\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"name\":\"extract\"},\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"\\n    <background>\\n      The user and agent have been brainstorming about their business idea.\\n    </background>\\n\\n    <available_topics>\\n      \\\"idea: The core business idea. What does the business do? What makes them different?\\\", \\\"audience: The target audience. What are their pain points? What are their goals?\\\", \\\"solution: How does the user's business solve the audience's pain points, or help them reach their goals?\\\", \\\"socialProof: Social proof or testimonials to include on the landing page. Remember, anything can be social proof: the user's background, experience, beliefs, founder story, etc.\\\", \\\"lookAndFeel: The look and feel of the landing page.\\\"\\n    </available_topics>\\n\\n    <task>\\n      Read the recent chat history, and summarize their answers,\\n      preserving as much information as possible. This will be used to generate \\n      persuasive marketing copy, so be sure to capture all the details.\\n\\n      If the user has answered MULTIPLE topics well, return an array of objects with the following shape:\\n      {\\n          topic: string,\\n          summary: string,\\n      }\\n    </task>\\n    \\n    <chat-history>\\n  <message>... 4 more messages...</message>\\n  <message>assistant: \\\"That's awesome! And what about your solution?\\\"</message>\\n  <message>human: \\\"My fitness program is specifically designed\\\"</message>\\n  <message>assistant: \\\"{\\\\n  \\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"helpMe\\\\\\\",\\\\n  \\\\\\\"text\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"Great start! I can see you're building something really compelling here. Let me help you articulate your solution more clearly and powerfully. Your program is specifically designed for this audience, but I want to make sure we capture exactly HOW it solves their pain points.\\\\\\\",\\\\n  \\\\\\\"template\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"My fitness program solves this by:\\\\\\\\n1. [Specific approach/methodology that addresses the \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"too old\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" belief]\\\\\\\\n2. [Specific approach/methodology that addresses the lack of fitness experience]\\\\\\\\n3. [Key differentiator that makes it work for 50+ men specifically]\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nFor example, it might include: beginner-friendly progressions, age-appropriate exercises, psychological coaching to overcome limiting beliefs, community support, etc.\\\\\\\",\\\\n  \\\\\\\"examples\\\\\\\": [\\\\n    \\\\\\\"A program that starts with foundational movements and gradually builds strength, specifically designed so complete beginners can succeed without feeling overwhelmed or injured\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"Personalized coaching that addresses the mental barrier of 'I'm too old' by showing real results from other men in their 50s who started from zero\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"Small group classes with peers their own age, so they don't feel out of place training alongside 25-year-olds\\\\\\\"\\\\n  ]\\\\n}\\\"</message>\\n  <message>human: \\\"To help men get started lifting, but using bodyweight exercises, and focusing on injury prevention\\\"</message>\\n</chat-history>\\n\\n    <output>\\n      Return an array of objects with the following shape:\\n      {\\n          topic: string,\\n          summary: string,\\n      }\\n    </output>\\n  \"}]}"
          },
          "queryString": [],
          "url": "https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages"
        },
        "response": {
          "bodySize": 902,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 902,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01SH4EquGsnGZSi9K4qHApXK\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_016rRfSXTtVM8WhBmjNbMjfw\",\"name\":\"extract\",\"input\":{\"output\":[{\"topic\":\"solution\",\"summary\":\"A fitness program specifically designed to help men get started with lifting using bodyweight exercises, with a strong focus on injury prevention. The program is tailored for men 50+ who believe they're too old or lack fitness experience, providing beginner-friendly progressions and age-appropriate exercises that allow complete beginners to succeed without feeling overwhelmed or injured.\"}]}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1440,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":127,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
          },
