          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 2556,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01A8FUp4YH3JBMx1eG2sPvdw\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01H4A6udUieYHJGShCUo6Aza\",\"name\":\"extract-54\",\"input\":{\"type\":\"helpMe\",\"text\":\"Perfect! Let me help you get specific about who you're targeting. We'll break this into clear pieces so you can paint a vivid picture of your ideal customer.\",\"template\":\"**1. Who are they?**\\n[Job title/role] at [company size/type], typically [age range or experience level]\\n\\n**2. What problems do they face?**\\n- They spend [how much time] on [specific task]\\n- They struggle with [specific pain point]\\n- This makes them feel [emotion: frustrated, overwhelmed, etc.]\\n\\n**3. What are they trying to achieve?**\\n- Their goal is to [desired outcome]\\n- They want to [specific aspiration related to their role]\\n- Success looks like [measurable result or feeling]\\n\\n**4. Why don't current solutions work?**\\n- They've tried [existing approach or tool]\\n- But it [specific limitation or gap]\",\"examples\":[\"**Podcast Host Example:**\\n1. Who: Independent podcast hosts or producers at mid-size shows (50K-500K downloads/month), typically 2-5 years into podcasting\\n2. Problems: Spend 8-10 hours per week sourcing guests through LinkedIn, Twitter, and email outreach. Feel frustrated by flaky guests and repetitive pitches. Anxious about content quality consistency.\\n3. Goals: Want to book high-quality, relevant guests in under 30 minutes. Want to grow their audience without hiring a producer.\\n4. Why existing solutions fail: Guest databases are outdated, LinkedIn is time-consuming, agencies are too expensive ($2K+/month)\",\"**Alternative Example - Corporate Podcast Producer:**\\n1. Who: Content/marketing managers at B2B SaaS companies (50-500 employees) launching or scaling internal podcasts\\n2. Problems: Spend 15+ hours weekly vetting guests, coordinating schedules, managing no-shows. Feel pressure to deliver consistent, high-caliber content. Frustrated by manual processes.\\n3. Goals: Want to build a sustainable guest pipeline that scales with their show. Want to focus on storytelling, not logistics.\\n4. Why existing solutions fail: Rolodex-building takes forever, agencies don't understand their niche, existing tools require manual data entry\"]}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3323,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":582,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
          },
