            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1391,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01Fx3p3wwcVsc7e79osWKTMY\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_012kQ8JSUj6KPur4zbXyoFnF\",\"name\":\"extract-59\",\"input\":{\"type\":\"reply\",\"text\":\"I appreciate the enthusiasm, but I can't do this for you—and honestly, that's a good thing! The best landing pages come from founders who deeply understand their own business idea. My job is to help you refine and sharpen your thinking, not to create something from thin air.\\n\\nLet's start with the foundation: **What's your business idea?** What problem are you solving, or what opportunity are you pursuing? What makes your approach different from what already exists?\\n\\nDon't worry about having it perfectly figured out—that's what this brainstorming session is for. Just tell me what you're thinking.\",\"examples\":[\"A SaaS tool that helps freelancers track time and invoicing automatically\",\"A premium dog training service focused on aggressive breeds\",\"An AI-powered meal planning app that adapts to dietary restrictions and budget\"],\"conclusion\":\"What's the core idea you want to test?\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2717,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":271,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
