        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1662,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1662,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01FVU4x1HgfvLtTodvvTL5f9\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_014vQRfbUffs1DGjidVndNEm\",\"name\":\"extract-63\",\"input\":{\"type\":\"reply\",\"text\":\"I appreciate the enthusiasm, but let's stay focused! 😊\\n\\nWe're working on **Friend of the Pod** — your podcast matchmaking service. I need to understand your business idea better so we can create compelling marketing copy.\\n\\nHere's what I'm trying to figure out: **What specific problem does Friend of the Pod solve, and who does it solve it for?**\\n\\nAre you helping podcast hosts find great guests? Helping people get on the right podcasts? Both? And what makes your approach different from existing solutions?\\n\\nGive me the real story behind this idea — what gap in the market did you notice?\",\"examples\":[\"We help indie authors find podcasts in their genre so they can promote their books to engaged audiences without spending weeks researching\",\"We connect B2B service providers (coaches, consultants, agencies) with podcasts that reach their ideal clients, making it easy for both sides\",\"We match podcast hosts with expert guests automatically, so hosts spend less time vetting and more time creating great content\"],\"conclusion\":\"I need you to articulate the core problem and who you're solving it for. That's the foundation of great marketing copy.\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2993,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":336,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
