            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_015VGveXM7sQ9VrtdaoXceRT\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_012uLeVGBME15rqoYAZoDegz\",\"name\":\"extract-65\",\"input\":{\"type\":\"reply\",\"text\":\"I hear you — but we need to get serious here! 😄\\n\\nYou came to me with **Friend of the Pod**, a podcast matchmaking service. That's a real business idea with potential, and I'm here to help you build something great.\\n\\nBut I can't create killer marketing copy if you're not engaged in the brainstorming process. So let's refocus.\\n\\n**Here's what I need from you:** Tell me about your podcast matchmaking service. Specifically:\\n- **Who are you helping?** (podcast hosts? guests? both?)\\n- **What problem are they facing?** (hard to find guests? hard to find the right podcasts? something else?)\\n- **Why does your solution matter?**\\n\\nThis is the foundation of everything. Without clarity here, we can't move forward. So what's it going to be — are you ready to build this, or should we call it a day?\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3310,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":252,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
