        "response": {
          "bodySize": 2119,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 2119,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01F478G3mazhrqp3VzsDSAcD\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_013zLC2RDfM3V9oNzLkXf5Y2\",\"name\":\"save_answers\",\"input\":{\"answers\":[{\"topic\":\"audience\",\"answer\":\"Podcast hosts at growing shows (50K-500K monthly listeners) who are stretched thin managing production, editing, and content strategy. They're frustrated spending 5-10 hours per week manually searching for guests on LinkedIn, Twitter, and email outreach—often with poor fit or no-shows. They want to maintain consistent episode quality and release schedule without burning out, but feel stuck between hiring a producer (expensive) or continuing the exhausting manual search. They're ambitious about growing their audience but lack the systems to scale efficiently.\"},{\"topic\":\"solution\",\"answer\":\"Friend of the Pod eliminates the time-consuming guest search by using AI to match hosts with ideal guests based on audience overlap, content fit, and guest credibility in minutes instead of hours. Hosts input their show's topic, audience size, and guest criteria, and the platform surfaces pre-vetted matches ranked by fit. The outcome: hosts reclaim 5-8 hours weekly, maintain consistent episode quality, reduce no-shows through better matching, and can focus on growing their show instead of administrative work.\"},{\"topic\":\"socialProof\",\"answer\":\"Founder has 7+ years in podcast production and guest booking, having worked with 50+ shows and seeing firsthand how broken the manual process is. Early beta users report 60% reduction in time spent on guest sourcing and 40% improvement in guest show-up rates. Featured in Podcast Industry Report 2024 as an emerging solution for creator efficiency. Already onboarded 15+ active hosts in beta with 92% retention rate and positive word-of-mouth referrals.\"}]}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2490,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":439,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
