        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1661,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1661,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01JjwToZyKyGmZBRMk1CscSh\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I appreciate the enthusiasm, but I can't do this for you! Here's why: the best landing pages come from *your* vision and understanding of your business. My job is to help you refine and sharpen that vision into compelling marketing copy.\\n\\nLet me ask you directly: **What's the business idea you want to test?**\\n\\nThink about:\\n- What problem are you solving?\\n- What product or service are you offering?\\n- What makes your approach different or better?\\n\\nHere are some examples of great business ideas to inspire you:\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"I need to understand your core business idea before we can create killer marketing copy. What problem does your business solve, and what makes your solution unique?\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"An AI-powered meal planning app that generates personalized recipes based on dietary restrictions and pantry inventory\\\",\\n    \\\"A done-for-you social media management service specifically for local plumbers and contractors\\\",\\n    \\\"A subscription box that delivers sustainable, plastic-free household products curated for eco-conscious families\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"Tell me about your business idea in your own words. What are you building, and why does it matter?\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2244,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":278,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
