            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1807,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01RdZuPDCv11gPdZQvpq8WQW\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\n\\nI like the concept, but I need to dig deeper to help you craft killer marketing copy. Let me ask you some clarifying questions:\\n\\n**What does \\\"podcast matchmaking\\\" actually mean?** Are you:\\n- Connecting podcast hosts with guests?\\n- Matching listeners with podcasts they'll love?\\n- Pairing podcasters with sponsors/advertisers?\\n- Something else entirely?\\n\\n**What makes Friend of the Pod different?** There are already some podcast discovery and guest-booking platforms out there. What's your unique angle or competitive advantage?\\n\\nOnce I understand the core mechanics and what sets you apart, we can build messaging that really resonates.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"I love the podcast matchmaking concept! But I need to understand the specifics. What exactly does Friend of the Pod do, and what makes it different from existing solutions?\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"We connect podcast hosts with the perfect guests using AI matching based on audience alignment and topic expertise\\\",\\n    \\\"We help listeners discover niche podcasts tailored to their interests through intelligent recommendation algorithms\\\",\\n    \\\"We match podcasters with sponsors whose products/services align with their audience demographics\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"Help me understand the core value proposition and what makes Friend of the Pod stand out in the market.\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2246,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":300,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
