        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1743,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1743,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_019Sc2hNuk8WLRUqdqaoXwMj\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I appreciate the enthusiasm, but let's stay focused! 😄\\n\\nI need you to help me understand your **Friend of the Pod** business idea so we can create compelling marketing copy for your landing page.\\n\\nLet me ask again more directly:\\n\\n**What problem does Friend of the Pod solve?** Who are you helping, and what's their pain point?\\n\\nFor example:\\n- Are you helping podcast hosts find great guests to interview?\\n- Are you helping guests get booked on relevant podcasts?\\n- Are you helping listeners discover podcasts they'll actually love?\\n\\nOnce I understand who you're serving and what problem you're solving, we can build a landing page that converts.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"I need to understand your core business idea for Friend of the Pod. What problem does it solve, and who does it solve it for?\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"We help podcast hosts find qualified guests who are experts in their niche and have engaged audiences\\\",\\n    \\\"We help authors, entrepreneurs, and thought leaders get booked on podcasts that reach their ideal customers\\\",\\n    \\\"We connect podcast listeners with shows they'll love based on their interests and listening habits\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"Tell me: Who are you helping, what's their main problem, and how does Friend of the Pod solve it?\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2546,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":304,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
