            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01Bb2MEzwKXt1XHNL1n3EfQH\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I hear you—pasta is delicious! But we need to focus here. 😊\\n\\nI'm a highly paid marketing consultant, and I've got a reputation to uphold. I can't help you build a landing page without understanding your actual business idea.\\n\\n**Let's get serious for a moment:** You came to me with \\\"Friend of the Pod\\\"—a podcast matchmaking service. That's a solid concept with real potential. But I need you to engage with me on the specifics so we can create marketing copy that actually converts.\\n\\nHere's what I need from you:\\n\\n**Who does Friend of the Pod serve?** (podcast hosts? guests? listeners?)\\n**What's their main pain point?** (hard to find guests? hard to get booked? hard to discover shows?)\\n**How does your service solve it?**\\n\\nGive me a real answer, and we'll build something great together. Otherwise, we're just wasting time.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"I need you to focus here. Tell me: Who does Friend of the Pod help, and what problem does it solve for them?\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"We help podcast hosts find guests quickly without spending hours vetting and cold-emailing\\\",\\n    \\\"We help entrepreneurs and experts get booked on podcasts that reach their target audience\\\",\\n    \\\"We help listeners discover hidden gem podcasts based on their specific interests\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"Pick one of these angles (or give me your own), and let's build from there.\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2873,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":348,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
